article.description: — Josh Bannan had a career-high 24 points plus 12 rebounds as Montana easily beat Omaha 68-47 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Bannan scores 24 to lead Montana past Omaha 68-47
article.linkText: Bannan scores 24 to lead Montana past Omaha 68-47
article.story: MISSOULA, Mont. -- — Josh Bannan had a career-high 24 points plus 12 rebounds as Montana easily beat Omaha 68-47 on Saturday night. Brandon Whitney had 13 points for Montana (2-2). Cameron Parker added six rebounds. Felix Lemetti had 10 points for the Mavericks (1-3). Nick Ferrarini added 10 points. Kyle Luedtke had six rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
